<h2>The legal bit</h2>
<p>The offer allows you to have 25% off one Urban session and 20% off your second session.</p>
<p>Participants need to be age 18 years or over. </p>
<p>Digital services are valid across the UK and face to face bookings are valid in London, Manchester, Birmingham.      </p>
<p>To redeem this offer, visit <a href="https://urban.co" target="_blank">www.urban.co </a> and enter your discount code at check out. Each code can be redeemed once per person.     </p>
